      "date": "2013-03-16 15:43:10.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/1117cf00-8e4f-11e2-a173-52540035b04c).  Ran 16 tests.  2 tests failed: lustre-rsync-test, sanity.",
